"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8566e4a06025f5c1c697930d8c2213f2a2a121","tid":2512231,"uid":387588,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"你其實係咪唔識分「係」同「喺」？"},{"pid":"6220798b2d13aaa33fb669a781d1e907560f9f16","tid":2512231,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"跟住落嚟係播映，《東張西望》之便秘放題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2512188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2512188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a520e2eb2c2c9583419ffb50e87fe0aa7f1eed23","tid":2512231,"uid":28503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"諗住做跟車地盤定洗碗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768a64fdf70a2238bfc929f0cb4d800e4e0dc2e5","tid":2512231,"uid":353267,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"今年大量fg 深黃掙住入點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc68c72b3e3d3e7248f686cb6b369febe7adc5e0","tid":2512231,"uid":226955,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"尊重大家作為黃營各司其職<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">只有五毛先最鐘意將黃營作為自己人嘅門檻set到超高然後打返黃營嘅人</span>，一句「相反香港人XXX，總之就係垃圾」，以踩低香港人，令香港人消磨意志，膠化思想呢種行為<br />\n<br />\n攬炒巴喺英國做咗咁多文宣突然變成食人血饅頭嘅契弟（已近乎成功抺黑）<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆當日明明係最後一個走反而比五毛笑「的士梁」笑足幾年<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元、沈旭暉等人去咗台灣，五毛就話佢地當香港手足係condom <br />\n<br />\n蘋果反共推動民主二十幾年，搞到畀中資同親中公司封殺廣告，老闆畀人拉埋（佢本身大可以晨早就飛走），咁都竟然唔係自己人（佢哋嘅邏輯係去台灣就係當手足condom，唔去台灣好似黎智英呢啲就係上一代弱智泛民係抵死），咁我想問邊個先係自己人，耶穌都未必做到自己人啦。<span class=\"red\"><strong>最慘就係總會有班弱智走去跟風連自己都講埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所有有爭議既議題就會扮哂兩邊去罵戰，放大分歧，令一般人覺得好煩，唔想理，少人參與討論之後五毛佢地自然就會主導咗輿論風向<br />\n<br />\n相關議題例如35+ 加泰集會 參與/杯葛選舉 黃店爭議 黃藍KOL<br />\n<br />\n之後就用以上議題去批評所有黃絲兼黃圈，用埋曬啲<span class=\"gold\">黃衛兵、連衛兵、時事台、cctoy、無腦黃絲...不斷用呢啲label 去標籤香港人</span>，班五毛其實醒過你我，新聞post五毛唔會咁用力，但係一有關於香港人身份或者香港人圍內嘅post佢地就會出盡全力分化同帶風向，加埋佢地平時啲風向post 就係想令連登變到香討咁"},{"pid":"4c8f2505ffa4b6c755efa5c8c387ab59df1697e0","tid":2512231,"uid":353267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a520e2eb2c2c9583419ffb50e87fe0aa7f1eed23","tid":2512231,"uid":28503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"諗住做跟車地盤定洗碗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"做政府 大把買左樓揾夠<br />\n賣左 幾千萬台灣 去台灣唔洗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e88594e183a67612c7ca9a53fbd95e86d07258","tid":2512231,"uid":32675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"宣誓真係好影響生涯規劃,以為會做過世既工變咗留低只係為搵多陣錢方便移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ceff5b80a82e72e70fe15cd4103ad3f9ce0c64","tid":2512231,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:05:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb2bc6fb55c9ea87491e20aeb18cad2aa6a4637","tid":2512231,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:06:01.000Z","msg":"共勉之"},{"pid":"bf908dcfa93fa89ab7780ac854a85739558d1816","tid":2512231,"uid":250291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"bdb09869dccef03073bacccc01bccc2928fbe646","tid":2512231,"uid":3873,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正公務員手足加油啦 唔好埋沒自己良知就夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f4485a0290e608e55f3770932d3d64fa75b9d7","tid":2512231,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202